item.title: You know what? The "clinginess" of male and female cats is not the same!
item.author: youremail@domain.com (Some Person)
item.description: Why are other cats so clingy, but your cat is a bit cold and impersonal? No matter how nice you are to your cat, it doesn’t seem to want to come near you. In fact, the degree of a cat’s clinginess is related to many factors. For example, the gender of the cat, the temperature of the weather, and whether the cat has needs. -01 Male cats are more clingy than female cats.
